{"tid":2349993,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"習近平汕頭企過嘅階磚被地方政府鑲金","createTime":"2021-01-02T03:41:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T15:40:20.000Z","uid":41343,"like":147,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"287d49dc823f421135180c9cefc955363b8b81da","tid":2349993,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T03:41:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210102/FVXGUBTUJ5D2THMDEDSMRCUE6Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210102%2FFVXGUBTUJ5D2THMDEDSMRCUE6Y%2F&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gTcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=2dc21384\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210102%2FFVXGUBTUJ5D2THMDEDSMRCUE6Y%2F&h=457649ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210102/FVXGUBTUJ5D2THMDEDSMRCUE6Y/</a>"},{"pid":"adcfb194d725fcda673b1a8ffbd8ec73bb19ab7a","tid":2349993,"uid":41343,"like":123,"dislike":2,"score":121,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T03:42:18.000Z","msg":"網上有片段顯示，在汕頭街頭，習近平出現過的地點被鋪上金色地磚，引來巿民圍觀。有街坊向《蘋果》表示，也有聽聞鋪金磚一事。有網民將「金磚」的照片發佈微博上，指這是習近平踩過的那一塊磚，磚上則標示了時間：「2020年10月13日17:00」。不少網民對此不以為然，認為「我的腦袋是習近平親自洗的，可能要被換成金的了」、「（習近平）肉體現代化了，思想還在皇上萬歲那一套」、「這是維尼捐了個地板，任千人踩萬人踏來贖罪嘛」、「包子皇帝又開始踩油門開倒車了，一腳油門回到古代」、「尿過的馬桶也換成金的吧」。"},{"pid":"abca20fe770cbac278c6a2a5e34b0838a23f1998","tid":2349993,"uid":66087,"like":119,"dislike":1,"score":118,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T03:48:00.000Z","msg":"睇片大部分大陸人當正習總係偶像 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"329a14c9b539c062e3dd89b5f12a163ef10fb599","tid":2349993,"uid":35699,"like":55,"dislike":2,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T03:50:22.000Z","msg":"可能係覺得踩污糟咗，不如拆咗佢換做金色磚，乾淨之餘又唔會hurt到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa6d4b54bbe307c0813ec4ed456d1d108028efad","tid":2349993,"uid":155095,"like":131,"dislike":0,"score":131,"citedBy":